data.description: PRICE REDUCED. LET'S GET THIS ONE IN ESCROW!! SELLER IS VERY MOTIVATED. You WILL love this home. It is located in a very desirable West side neighborhood. It features all the amenities you can ask for in a home and property. There is a great view, RV access, open floor plan, a modern kitchen with granite counter tops and newer appliances. In addition to all this, there is full in-law suite featuring a separate entrance, full kitchen, bathroom, bedroom and living room. To top it all off, there is solar power and a fire suppression system which will greatly reduce utility and insurance costs.
